<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Personal | Panagiotis Kaliosis</title><link>https://pkaliosis.github.io/tag/personal.html</link><atom:link href="https://pkaliosis.github.io/tag/personal/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><description>Personal</description><generator>Wowchemy (https://wowchemy.com)</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 29 Jun 2023 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><image><url>https://pkaliosis.github.io/media/logo_hub4241536a40aba19023fe53b0ae22453_4788_300x300_fit_lanczos_3.png</url><title>Personal</title><link>https://pkaliosis.github.io/tag/personal.html</link></image><item><title>I have obtained a position at French CNRS</title><link>https://pkaliosis.github.io/news/2023-cnrs-start.html</link><pubDate>Thu, 29 Jun 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pkaliosis.github.io/news/2023-cnrs-start.html</guid><description>&lt;p>In the continuity of my MSCA fellowship, I&amp;rsquo;ve been hired by the French CNRS (Section 11) as a tenured full time researcher at &lt;a href="https://liphy.univ-grenoble-alpes.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LIPhy&lt;/a> (UGA).&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>We ranked 1st and 3rd in the Caption task of this year's competition.</title><link>https://pkaliosis.github.io/news/clef-distinction/clef-distinction.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 10 May 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pkaliosis.github.io/news/clef-distinction/clef-distinction.html</guid><description>&lt;p>We participated in the annual &lt;a href="https://www.imageclef.org/2023/medical/caption" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ImageCLEFmedical Caption&lt;/a> competition, where we ranked 1st in the Concept Detection and 3rd in the Caption Prediction task. This is a distinction that our group has been systematically achieving for the last few years. You can read more &lt;a href="https://www.athenarc.gr/en/news/distinction-international-artificial-intelligence-competition" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here&lt;/a>.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>